{"word":"βόστρυχος","slug":"βόστρυχος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βόστρυχος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βότρυς'><el>βότρυς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a curl</i> or <i>lock of hair</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>anything twisted</i> or <i>wreathed</i>, <el>πυρὸς β.</el>, of <i>a flash of lightning</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}